    "originContent": "Current features:<br/>",
    "translatedContent": "当前功能：<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 4,
    "rowsha": "82FisxssHH9QVP0fzyUV6YDeXkaI5eR2fnpduN1qJek=",
    "originContent": " * Use (Shift+)AltGr+Key to type Mathematical Symbols (Refer to AMaDiA_ReplacementTables)<br/>",
    "translatedContent": " * 使用 (Shift+)AltGr+键 来输入数学符号（参考 AMaDiA_ReplacementTables）<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 5,
    "rowsha": "ADaHJu0nsk9yb+WT4ybdg+Y7Go2K2dtcCjITK2ctFso=",
    "originContent": " * Tab 1 : Scientific Calculator<br/>",
    "translatedContent": " * 选项卡 1 ：科学计算器<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 6,
    "rowsha": "gprWJetY6UrTi1PorRPZZ+mb782ULcicpIf8QCg5lgE=",
    "originContent": "   * Calculate with +,-,±,×,÷,√,^,°, Integral f(x) dx, d(f(x))/dx, y'(x), complex numbers, sin(), cos(), tan(), exp(), log() , π , E and more<br/>",
    "translatedContent": "   * 使用 +,-,±,×,÷,√,^,°, 积分 f(x) dx, 导数 d(f(x))/dx, y'(x), 复数, sin(), cos(), tan(), exp(), log() , π , E 等进行计算<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 7,
    "rowsha": "E6T7cdWavclw5XfdC/gZNm4Gtqud1twFhtopAbCCgbM=",
    "originContent": "   * Solve an equation with unknown variables<br/>",
    "translatedContent": "   * 解含未知变量的方程<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 8,
    "rowsha": "JeLCS8BxqpvaJNq2AAFlb6x0uvF1A10WnBBVQgTIGxk=",
    "originContent": "   * Solve Differential Equations (including particular solutions)<br/>",
    "translatedContent": "   * 解微分方程（包括特解）<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 9,
    "rowsha": "7FV16DhQ7rgYtf8Vy38uWzdwLPlT4flaoCukutaHOwg=",
    "originContent": "   * Test for equality of two terms<br/>",
    "translatedContent": "   * 测试两个表达式是否相等<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 10,
    "rowsha": "Hc7WfeUdy/pQf/YNicax7uBxZGD/1rQWWTH67aQRaPU=",
    "originContent": "   * Use mathematic Unicode symbols to type faster!<br/>",
    "translatedContent": "   * 使用数学Unicode符号更快输入！<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 11,
    "rowsha": "W8B3WL10PEuJzGrUWVj0iRrH9tViCnu3V60vBObFwXQ=",
    "originContent": "   * Turn on units in the options to do things like convert_to(7foot+3inch,m)<br/>",
    "translatedContent": "   * 在选项中开启单位支持以执行如 convert_to(7foot+3inch,m) 的操作<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 12,
    "rowsha": "KFcQqn+EwZryK2eA9iELGyd7GbnidMuZaQb+s9qgMps=",
    "originContent": "   * For more detailed usage check out Help/Examples and copy/paste the examples to the according tab input fields<br/>",
    "translatedContent": "   * 更多详细用法请查看帮助/示例，并将示例复制粘贴到相应的选项卡输入栏<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 13,
    "rowsha": "myq82/7nYVZ1BhQKfhuXxQMTABL+FNh7SQBeVvR2U8I=",
    "originContent": " * Tab 2 : Convert input to LaTeX and display it<br/>",
    "translatedContent": " * 选项卡 2 ：将输入转换为LaTeX并显示<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 14,
    "rowsha": "okQ4CBXBSZDnpsesmLBUuJOfPSS5sZMdHa8fsv3q3eo=",
    "originContent": " * Tab 3 : Plot 2D Graphs (3D and complex Graphs are WIP)<br/>",
    "translatedContent": " * 选项卡 3 ：绘制二维图形（3D和复数图形正在开发中）<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 15,
    "rowsha": "bjROTHJ4rqAb6PJOeuNygC0S31plumaC2qSFTlI4zeI=",
    "originContent": " * Tab 4 : Equations with matrices and vectors as well as systems of linear equations<br/>",
    "translatedContent": " * 选项卡 4 ：包含矩阵和向量的方程，以及线性方程组<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 16,
    "rowsha": "breKsuBNgfartt3h3ad6zxHQ38TLue33+PCsL22RTUY=",
    "originContent": " * System Control Window : Everything for System Control (WIP)<br/>",
    "translatedContent": " * 系统控制窗口 ：系统控制相关功能（开发中）<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 17,
    "rowsha": "8+awOkZ8HhT1ho/LgFaFeDl+CZRCfHcOisSEbiJYiqY=",
    "originContent": " * LAN chat program (needs overhaul)<br/>",
    "translatedContent": " * 局域网聊天程序（需重构）<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 18,
    "rowsha": "neleO1WnMCP3SLopIg/4DbwXikSAL1fgEAMRWnA4uGw=",
    "originContent": "   * Intended for sharing equations with other users in the same network to make cooperative working easier<br/>",
    "translatedContent": "   * 用于在同一网络内用户之间共享方程，方便协作工作<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 19,
    "rowsha": "eORI05Pt1XqlMnziBjW9DbrBSbXOtqHA6WFql773diU=",
    "originContent": "   * Separate Server and Client applications<br/>",
    "translatedContent": "   * 独立的服务器和客户端应用<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 20,
    "rowsha": "8Salww8Ojmqj5tSV7j641omHnAbyvvog2Dzf448gDsg=",
    "originContent": "   * Allows sending of text and text files<br/>",
    "translatedContent": "   * 支持发送文本和文本文件<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 21,
    "rowsha": "9wLXPXw6+3hnJrdSqEMbyxcFm3uyQoMANoq9IbfQGWQ=",
    "originContent": "   * Share text files with all other users in the network via drag'n'drop into the input field<br/>",
    "translatedContent": "   * 通过拖放文本文件到输入框与网络内所有用户共享<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 22,
    "rowsha": "5mWyuGL1WbQ2Xc1hZWjdPx92MSKmCBGw2e4PTkkFEZE=",
    "originContent": "   * Server has some moderation tools (Muting/Kicking/Banning<br/>",
    "translatedContent": "   * 服务器具备部分管理工具（禁言/踢出/封禁）<br/>"
  },
