    "rowsha": "4rMyl2+YeNcZ6LtiyiZ0b7GE368mR8eJPXfc8mV30oA=",
    "originContent": "# How to Install",
    "translatedContent": "# 安装方法"
  },
  {
    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "Rl0OeMAhztS/Ba2lHiiuKH4ramyz+AKgutO7oUUzt0c=",
    "originContent": "On Windows:<br/>",
    "translatedContent": "在Windows上：<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "WJaLNT6lMbpJGK5UDOA0EmSotznaj7cf2OgqEOOi6eY=",
    "originContent": " * Install https://gitforwindows.org/<br/>",
    "translatedContent": " * 安装 https://gitforwindows.org/<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 34,
    "rowsha": "EtTDaIbbP9FTAzyAuUUDM+0JMTiO8cE0Zy6UISsJ1jc=",
    "originContent": " * Install https://www.anaconda.com/distribution/<br/>",
    "translatedContent": " * 安装 https://www.anaconda.com/distribution/<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 35,
    "rowsha": "dFuBe4giZFn6sMbvm6glnF/Iy9LskDxipPmoaFRkacY=",
    "originContent": " * Create two files \"AMaDiA.bat\" and \"AMaDiA_INSTALL.bat\" and copy the text from the two file in WINDOWS-INSTALL into them by rightcklicking on them and selecting the modify option<br/>",
    "translatedContent": " * 创建两个文件 \"AMaDiA.bat\" 和 \"AMaDiA_INSTALL.bat\"，并从 WINDOWS-INSTALL 文件夹中将相应文件的内容复制到这两个文件中，右键点击选择“编辑”即可<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 36,
    "rowsha": "yHLqcKoaaash6U7F1O6/bH+55elDOYA74czSBnrB2YY=",
    "originContent": " * doubleclick on \"AMaDiA_INSTALL.bat\" to install AMaDiA (The installation location is the user folder. This can be changed by editing both files.)<br/>",
    "translatedContent": " * 双击 \"AMaDiA_INSTALL.bat\" 安装 AMaDiA（安装位置为用户文件夹，可通过编辑这两个文件更改）<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 37,
    "rowsha": "WISfBGyqvco3bVaygPMNwq7fQUBL3mGuajpc9PVbtcI=",
    "originContent": " * From now on doubleclicking on AMaDiA.bat will update and then run AMaDiA<br/>",
    "translatedContent": " * 以后双击 AMaDiA.bat 将会更新并运行 AMaDiA<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 38,
    "rowsha": "Nqnn8clbgv+5l0PgxcTOldg8mkMKrFn4TvPL+rYUUGg=",
    "originContent": " ",
